---
title: Chicken Katsu & Garlic Rice with Roasted Courgette & Slaw
description: If you want your kitchen to smell amazing you don’t need to pull out every spice you own, just a simple katsu sauce, garlic rice
and roasted courgette will do. With a golden crumbed chicken, it’s enough to have your senses blissfully overwhelmed with fragrances that leave your mouth watering.
